text.#text:
Whereas, on November 30, 1999, the Speaker of the House of
			 Representatives signed an agreement with the leaders of the Parliament of
			 Ukraine to establish an interparliamentary exchange program between the two
			 legislative bodies;

Whereas Members of the House of Representatives and the
			 Parliament of Ukraine have already participated in video teleconferences as
			 part of this agreement; and
